transcript:
Customer: ویڈیو! اسلام علیکم!
Customer: Bye.
Agent: Wa Alaikum Assalam, mein Ahmed bol raha hoon UBL se. Aap ki madad kese kar sakta hoon?
Customer: احمد مجھے اپنی بیلنس انکوائری کرنی ہے
Agent: Zaroor, ab barah-e-karam apna TPIN batayen.
Agent: Shukriya. Ab verification ke liye apna account number batayen.
Agent: Aap ke account ka balance 0 rupee hai. Agar aap ka koi aur sawal ho to batayen.
Agent: UBL call karne ka shukriya. Allah Hafiz!
Agent: Allah Hafiz!
Customer: MBC 뉴스 이덕영입니다.
Customer: Okay, I've changed the account number to 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 this is the thing I'll tell the chatbot the second thing I want to do is a word if the if anything else other than this account number
Customer: It should say that the account doesn't exist or something.
Agent: Maazrat chahta hoon, yeh baat main madad nahi kar sakta. Agar aap ko koi aur maloomat chahiye, barah-e-karam UBL branch se raabta karein. Allah Hafiz.
